procession of singing samaritans at their holy mountain slaying and 
scattering them wantonly 
because of such ruthlessness jews customarily spat whenever a 
roman soldier passed however this peculiarly crowdrousing jesus 
apparently didnt hate the military something the waiting centurion 
had learned from fellow officers 
