democracy gorbachev style preempted the movie king kong in 
the palace of culture of this port city 1000 miles north of moscow 
famed as the destination of the world war ii allied convoys carrying 
guns and spam to the embattled soviets 
in snowcoated kirov palace where on other days the great ape 
